Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.20,0:02:08.17,biaoti,NTP,0,0,0,,被邀請的　觀光者
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.47,0:02:17.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千影小姐的家在懸崖那邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.46,0:02:19.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯　馬上就到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.50,0:02:27.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原來是洋館
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.37,0:02:30.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這島上僅此一座
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.70,0:02:35.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,據說本來是為了漂流到這裡的西洋人而建造的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.93,0:02:39.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但想讓我看的東西是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.09,0:02:47.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,打擾了　我是行人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.28,0:02:49.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.95,0:02:54.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千影小姐有姐姐或者妹妹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.10,0:02:58.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上就來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.28,0:03:01.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊　是指帕娜子小姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.24,0:03:04.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,請稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.91,0:03:10.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.05,0:03:12.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行…行人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.03,0:03:15.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.42,0:03:23.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你…好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.63,0:03:26.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊　對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.87,0:03:30.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人　沒關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.57,0:03:33.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,來了呢　行人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.94,0:03:36.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也讓我做各種觀察吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.69,0:03:41.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼得快點做歡迎的準備了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.71,0:03:44.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,請用
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.92,0:03:47.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是在千影家做女傭的帕娜子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.14,0:03:50.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.45,0:03:53.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊　真的不用介意了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.09,0:03:54.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,帕娜子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.37,0:03:59.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是公認的會照顧人脾氣又好　島上第一的美少女
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.70,0:04:04.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,島上第一的美少女
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.16,0:04:15.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行　想像的翅膀無法伸展
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.54,0:04:19.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,料理的手藝也很厲害　也許也是島上第一
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.74,0:04:21.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那還真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.31,0:04:24.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要這樣　好害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.21,0:04:29.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊　我真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.43,0:04:32.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起　對不起　對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.15,0:04:34.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧　行人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.01,0:04:36.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.86,0:04:40.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,帕娜子小姐有時會不由自主的做些意外的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.55,0:04:45.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.44,0:04:50.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,腰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.80,0:04:52.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,胸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.19,0:04:55.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,背
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.79,0:04:59.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千影想讓人看的東西是
