Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.02,0:05:13.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個打扮是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.93,0:05:16.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啦　不喜歡嗎
