Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.48,0:05:24.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,進了好的鮑魚哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.84,0:05:29.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼　現在開始
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.77,0:05:31.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.97,0:05:31.99,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,非常好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.79,0:05:41.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人　如何
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.44,0:05:42.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,連小鈴都
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.06,0:05:49.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺很有趣　但這個胸部有點緊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.78,0:05:51.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.05,0:05:55.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.61,0:05:58.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要被姐姐大人詛咒了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.79,0:06:01.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣真的可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.54,0:06:04.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對我來說只是便裝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.05,0:06:06.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,便裝嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.24,0:06:10.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但怎麼想這都是最好的cosplay啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.31,0:06:14.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來　為什麼要穿成那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.13,0:06:19.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為書上說會讓行人高興
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.61,0:06:20.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,書？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.51,0:06:22.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是　在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.85,0:06:24.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,廚師　熊貓
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.74,0:06:27.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巫女　還有少婦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.98,0:06:31.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不能參考這種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.03,0:06:35.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是為什麼島上會有這種書
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.55,0:06:36.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊　那是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.99,0:06:39.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,暴風雨來的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.31,0:06:45.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,海浪常常會把漂流在島附近海外的東西吸進來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.31,0:07:05.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,除了剛才的書之外還有許多東西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.63,0:07:07.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想讓行人看看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.02,0:07:09.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯　可以
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.82,0:07:11.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,幫了大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.81,0:07:18.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,漂流過來的東西中最感興趣的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.06,0:07:21.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是行人你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.04,0:07:24.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.61,0:07:29.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哇　好多數量的書
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.02,0:07:32.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在這裡的只是少數
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.92,0:07:36.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,漂流到藍蘭島上的書都在家裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.14,0:07:39.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,光這裡就象圖書館了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.96,0:07:43.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千影是島上最有知識的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.31,0:07:45.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還教過大家知識
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.49,0:07:49.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼　想讓我看的東西是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.02,0:07:52.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,首先是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.71,0:07:54.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,桶？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.77,0:07:56.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊　是電飯煲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.94,0:07:58.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,電…飯煲？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.80,0:08:01.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只要把米放裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.39,0:08:03.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,按下按鈕飯就做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.62,0:08:05.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊　真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.99,0:08:07.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要用火嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.89,0:08:10.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼　這個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.13,0:08:12.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是微波爐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.81,0:08:17.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把食物和飲料放進去按下按鈕就能變熱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.43,0:08:19.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這種像金庫一樣的東西？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.89,0:08:21.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不需要火嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.49,0:08:22.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.77,0:08:27.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,按這個按鈕…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.97,0:08:29.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對我來說可能是很平常的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.41,0:08:33.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過對她們來說就像未知物體
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.47,0:08:37.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺有點新鮮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.80,0:08:41.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,來到這島上一直都是我在吃驚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.76,0:08:45.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,外面的世界文明居然發展成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.81,0:08:48.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呐　行人快點來用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.78,0:08:50.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個能做飯的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.31,0:08:54.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊　我也想看看如何工作的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.01,0:08:59.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不能用嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.50,0:09:02.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為這個島上沒有電吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.22,0:09:07.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個電是指能讓街燈發亮的erekitere發電機嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.74,0:09:09.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ereki…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.10,0:09:10.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛　差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.03,0:09:14.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在的文明使用的物品沒有電是沒有用的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.85,0:09:18.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼在這裡的這些
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.84,0:09:19.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這些
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.65,0:09:20.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這些
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.84,0:09:22.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這些都…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.49,0:09:24.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯　只是垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.20,0:09:33.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊　變白了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.25,0:09:35.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是做了不好的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.95,0:09:38.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,垃…垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.52,0:09:40.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,垃圾房子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.03,0:09:44.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.92,0:09:49.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過只要知道了他們的真實情況就打住吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.43,0:09:51.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然能做出這種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.62,0:09:53.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,外面的文明真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.95,0:09:55.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼　差不多回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.80,0:09:57.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯　對呐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.30,0:09:59.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊　要回去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.94,0:10:02.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯　因為還得做飯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.03,0:10:05.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊　是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.86,0:10:07.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過目的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.73,0:10:14.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊　不好　關鍵的行人的觀察還沒…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.43,0:10:17.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等等…　等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.67,0:10:20.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不介意的話住下來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.17,0:10:22.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,住下來？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.12,0:10:23.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.05,0:10:23.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦　小鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.00,0:10:26.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,晚飯也已經準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.61,0:10:30.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,飯後的甜點也準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.53,0:10:31.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,紅豆大福
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.03,0:10:33.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,紅豆大福
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.17,0:10:38.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呐呐　就接受邀請留下來吃飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.31,0:10:40.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好嗎　行人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.48,0:10:44.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那不客氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.25,0:10:45.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.24,0:10:47.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼請稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.43,0:10:56.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,難得好久沒有動手做料理
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.63,0:10:59.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要讓行人飽吃一頓
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.26,0:11:03.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過說回來全是不可思議的料理呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.15,0:11:05.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,漢堡包
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.16,0:11:07.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,拉麵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.37,0:11:09.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,魚貝雞米飯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.37,0:11:09.37,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（燴肉飯上澆上含入魚貝，\N蘑菇的白色醬汁後在烤箱中烤制的菜肴）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.74,0:11:10.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,奶油麵包
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.47,0:11:11.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,黃油
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.36,0:11:12.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鵝肝菜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.34,0:11:13.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,羅宋湯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.71,0:11:16.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都不太知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.01,0:11:26.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,建築是西式　果然食物也是西式吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.18,0:11:28.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,西式？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.28,0:11:32.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊　是指西洋的食物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.50,0:11:34.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,會出來什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.80,0:11:35.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,烤蝦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.04,0:11:37.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,海鮮火鍋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.16,0:11:39.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,義大利面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.20,0:11:42.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還是說咖哩飯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.68,0:11:49.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.87,0:11:53.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,按照行人所留下的島外的菜單所做的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.96,0:11:54.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.20,0:11:57.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那請吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.04,0:12:07.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…這是…什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.00,0:12:09.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是漢堡包
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.44,0:12:11.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,漢…漢堡包？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.58,0:12:12.26,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}煎餅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.58,0:12:12.26,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}菠菜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.13,0:12:16.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,煎餅和豆腐真配
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.82,0:12:19.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真好吃呢　這漢堡包
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.09,0:12:21.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.66,0:12:23.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼下面的料理
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.21,0:12:25.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是拉麵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.13,0:12:27.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯　是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.98,0:12:29.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個看起來很像
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.99,0:12:31.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.73,0:12:37.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這面是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.76,0:12:44.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,噢　{\fnzhunyuan\fs27\b1}蒟蒻{\r}粉絲原來還有這種烏冬一樣的吃法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.85,0:12:49.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛　就像方便麵一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.62,0:12:53.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.65,0:12:54.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千影小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.76,0:12:55.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.72,0:12:56.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是章魚燒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.98,0:12:58.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,章魚燒？　好大
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.15,0:13:06.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊　動了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.23,0:13:08.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊咧　還是活的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.46,0:13:10.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把活章魚放進去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.80,0:13:11.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.84,0:13:12.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.14,0:13:20.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.91,0:13:22.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.65,0:13:24.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有這心意就很高興了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.76,0:13:29.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上就去做些其他東西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.55,0:13:30.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.83,0:13:32.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,普通的飯就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.66,0:13:34.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,普通　比如？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.28,0:13:38.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢　像咖哩飯一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.85,0:13:41.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這島上沒有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.96,0:13:44.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,魚咖哩就不是飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.64,0:13:46.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有的　咖哩飯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.62,0:13:47.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.56,0:13:49.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個很辣的東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.96,0:13:52.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不擅長吃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.44,0:13:53.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.99,0:13:55.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有咖哩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.64,0:13:56.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊　是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.05,0:14:01.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咖哩飯是在「文明開化」的時候進入日本的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.64,0:14:05.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咖哩原來是那麼有歷史的食物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.01,0:14:08.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼　一份咖哩飯就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.32,0:14:10.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.05,0:14:15.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哇　咖哩飯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.03,0:14:17.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.96,0:14:23.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如何　合你口味嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.20,0:14:31.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…太…好吃了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.75,0:14:33.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.90,0:14:35.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好辣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.77,0:14:36.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,請用
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.10,0:14:39.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,紅豆大福
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.35,0:14:44.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯　真幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.16,0:14:50.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真沒想到能在這島上吃到咖哩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.94,0:14:55.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊咧　時間過得比預想的要快
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.23,0:14:57.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼還是回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.49,0:14:59.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在…在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.14,0:15:02.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然還是不好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.50,0:15:05.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且家裡攢了許多衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.17,0:15:08.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行　現在才是正式的觀察
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.25,0:15:10.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,觀察？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.39,0:15:11.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,正式是？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.81,0:15:15.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊　那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.22,0:15:17.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.23,0:15:23.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的話　就算強硬手段也要讓他們住下來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.16,0:15:27.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊　章魚在頭上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.43,0:15:34.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啦　對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.65,0:15:35.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.97,0:15:40.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,請吧　這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.71,0:15:41.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.25,0:16:01.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我就…在你們兩個洗好後進來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.83,0:16:11.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人一直都不和我一起洗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.17,0:16:13.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.64,0:16:16.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還一直噴鼻血
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.33,0:16:17.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.71,0:16:20.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是出乎計算之外
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.78,0:16:25.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,本來還打算在為行人擦背的時候做各種調查
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.75,0:16:30.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,算了　還有其他手段
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.36,0:16:31.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,夜晚還很長
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.01,0:16:44.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣泡著　只會增大對行人的探知心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.93,0:16:45.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,增大…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.00,0:16:55.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,偶爾在別人家裡洗澡也好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.83,0:16:58.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,盯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.83,0:17:00.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了　千影
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.62,0:17:04.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想起探知心來了　對小鈴胸部的急速成長
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.99,0:17:08.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也已經非常在意了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.68,0:17:10.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那手是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.14,0:17:14.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,順便讓我來調查一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.59,0:17:23.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哪天真的會死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.03,0:17:28.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人　洗好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.04,0:17:30.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那我進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.67,0:17:45.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巨大的浴室真舒爽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.39,0:17:48.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.42,0:17:54.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不能一起進去的話　那就偷窺好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.27,0:17:57.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過沒有眼睛好難看清
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.89,0:17:59.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,靠近點看的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.89,0:18:10.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.30,0:18:16.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我來幫你擦背吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.74,0:18:18.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊　帕娜子小姐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.09,0:18:20.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.32,0:18:21.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.66,0:18:25.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎　那麼拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.62,0:18:30.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,帕娜子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.95,0:18:35.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人不介意帕娜子小姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.30,0:18:38.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼我和小鈴卻…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.12,0:18:43.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊　好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.05,0:18:45.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,非常對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.87,0:18:49.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,機會　帕娜子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.07,0:18:50.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,做得好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.18,0:18:52.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,趁機調查行人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.72,0:18:59.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,圓滑的男生輪廓
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.54,0:19:02.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不錯的肌肉體質
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.28,0:19:04.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,胸部也還可以
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.14,0:19:07.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是男人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.19,0:19:11.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了　忽然心跳加速了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.96,0:19:13.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是泡的太長了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.76,0:19:16.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝　帕娜子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.06,0:19:22.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊　好險
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.97,0:19:29.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然在遠處看不清
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.80,0:19:31.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然有點危險…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.32,0:19:41.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,絕佳的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.69,0:19:58.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,帕娜子小姐也來泡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.35,0:19:59.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.31,0:20:11.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,帕娜子小姐應該安靜點進來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.06,0:20:13.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊　對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.30,0:20:34.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千…千影
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.59,0:20:40.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好重
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.62,0:20:42.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.01,0:20:44.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說是泡久了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.06,0:20:45.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上就會好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.19,0:20:48.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,結果還是住下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.55,0:20:51.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.57,0:20:56.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我做了什麼讓小鈴生氣的事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.90,0:21:01.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在浴室　就把我當做沒必要的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.79,0:21:06.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是　我完全不知道千影躲在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.36,0:21:09.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,帕娜子小姐不也一起了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.21,0:21:11.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯　怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.51,0:21:16.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原來行人說男人和女人洗澡要分開是騙人的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.18,0:21:20.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,帕娜子小姐是大象啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.35,0:21:23.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不管大象還是人　女孩子就是女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.24,0:21:27.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的　在和我一起洗澡之前不原諒你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.29,0:21:29.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.49,0:22:55.24,biaoti,NTP,0,0,0,,{\3c&HE7A573}「想要迷惑他…繼承人」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.97,0:23:04.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,男人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.32,0:23:07.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,人類性別來說是男性
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.60,0:23:10.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又和動植物中的雄性同義詞
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.76,0:23:14.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在體現勇敢勇猛的情況下使用
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.55,0:23:18.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,謎團越來越多了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.19,0:23:22.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人　接下來也讓我繼續調查吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.82,0:23:29.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有去洗澡也會頭暈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.71,0:23:32.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是個謎團
